OL,3,CIsrael 'ready for any scenario' as
OL,4,Cforces continue to push in Lebanon
OL,6,FIsraeli troops continue their push
OL,7,Finto Lebanon with bombardment in the
OL,8,Fsouth of the country not letting up,
OL,9,Fas ITV News Correspondent John Ray
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FIsraeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,13,FNetanyahu has said forces will
OL,14,Fcontinue to fight in Lebanon,
OL,15,Fconcentrating on the strategic town of
OL,16,FBint Jbeil in southern Lebanon.
OL,18,FHe said Israeli troops are about to
OL,19,F"eliminate this great stronghold of
OL,20,FHezbollah".
OL,26,@{D@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
