FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776330350
OL,3,CIsrael 'ready for any scenario' as
OL,4,Cforces continue to push in Lebanon
OL,6,FIn a video address on Wednesday
OL,7,Fevening Netanyahu said he has given
OL,8,Finstructions for the military to
OL,9,Fcontinue to widen the security zone in
OL,10,Fsouth Lebanon - a reference to areas
OL,11,Fclose to the border that the Israeli
OL,12,Farmy now occupies - and to spread it
OL,13,Feastward.
OL,15,FHe said Israel is concurrently
OL,16,Fnegotiating with Lebanon, with two
OL,17,Fcentral goals: disarming Hezbollah and
OL,18,Fa sustainable peace. "Peace through
OL,19,Fstrength," he added.
OL,26,@zD@VOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
