OL,3,CIsrael 'ready for any scenario' as
OL,4,Cforces continue to push in Lebanon
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, earlier on Wednesday, three
OL,12,Fdifferent teams of paramedics were
OL,13,Fstruck in southern Lebanon, the
OL,14,Fcountry's health ministry said, as
OL,15,FIsrael pressed ahead with its aerial
OL,16,Fand ground offensive.
OL,18,FThe attacks in southern Lebanon killed
OL,19,Fthree paramedics, wounded six others
OL,20,Fand left a fourth medic missing in the
OL,21,Ftown of Mayfadoun.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776330350
OL,3,CIsrael 'ready for any scenario' as
OL,4,Cforces continue to push in Lebanon
OL,6,FThe ministry said Israel struck the
OL,7,Ffirst team of paramedics on Wednesday
OL,8,Fas it was heading to rescue wounded
OL,9,Fpeople, killing one paramedic.
OL,11,FAnother medical worker on that initial
OL,12,Fmission remains "missing," the
OL,13,Fministry said, without elaborating.
OL,15,FIsrael struck the second team as it
OL,16,Frushed to rescue the first, wounding
OL,17,Fthree more paramedics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776330350
OL,3,CIsrael 'ready for any scenario' as
OL,4,Cforces continue to push in Lebanon
OL,6,FIn the third and final rescue attempt,
OL,7,FIsrael again hit ambulances heading to
OL,8,Fthe site, killing two paramedics and
OL,9,Fwounding three more.
OL,11,FThe Israeli military did not
OL,12,Fimmediately respond to a request for
OL,13,Fcomment on the strikes.
OL,15,FLebanon's health ministry denounced
OL,16,FIsrael's attacks as "a flagrant crime"
OL,17,Fand warned that "paramedics have
OL,18,Fbecome direct targets, pursued
OL,19,Frelentlessly in a blatant violation
OL,20,F(of) ... international humanitarian
OL,21,Flaw."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776330350
OL,3,CIsrael 'ready for any scenario' as
OL,4,Cforces continue to push in Lebanon
OL,6,FMore than 2,167 people have been
OL,7,Fkilled by Israeli strikes on Lebanon
OL,8,Fsince March 2, according to Lebanon's
OL,9,Fhealth ministry.
OL,11,FThe prime minister said that the US
OL,12,Fwas updating Israel on the talks with
OL,13,FIran and that Israel was prepared for
OL,14,Fany scenario, should the fighting with
OL,15,FIran resume.
OL,17,FIt comes as a US naval blockade came
OL,18,Finto place on Monday, according to the
OL,19,Fcountry's military, which "completely
OL,20,Fhalted economic trade going into and
OL,21,Fout of Iran by sea".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776330350
OL,3,CIsrael 'ready for any scenario' as
OL,4,Cforces continue to push in Lebanon
OL,6,FThe blockade started on Monday
OL,7,Fafternoon after the Iran effectively
OL,8,Fclosed the Strait of Hormuz more than
OL,9,Fa month ago.
OL,11,FUS President Donald Trump's
OL,12,Fannouncement of a blockade came after
OL,13,Fnegotiations between Iran and the US,
OL,14,Fheld in Pakistan, failed to reach a
OL,15,Fbreakthrough over the weekend.
OL,17,FThe White House said on Wednesday the
OL,18,FUS has not requested an extension to
OL,19,Fthe ceasefire but discussions between
OL,20,FIran and the US are "productive and
OL,21,Fongoing".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
